hive.org/web/20200821103725/https://novacrystallis.com/2017/02/final-fantasy-xiv-stormblood-interview-naoki-yoshida/|dead-url=no}}</ref>对于场景，吉田认为玩家会根据故事的方向期待阿拉米格，所以开发者们力推加入一个全新的领域来给他们惊喜。<ref>{{Cite web|title=Final Fantasy XIV: Stormblood Interview -- Naoki Yoshida Talks Story, PS4 Pro, Level Boost and Much More|url=https://www.dualshockers.com/final-fantasy-xiv-stormblood-interview-naoki-yoshida/|accessdate=2020-12-05|date=2017-06-01|work=DualShockers|language=en|archive-date=2020-11-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201112035550/https://www.dualshockers.com/final-fantasy-xiv-stormblood-interview-naoki-yoshida/|dead-url=no}}</ref>艺术团队有意设计了多玛和紫州的两种不同类型的日本美学之间的对比，而不是简单地复制大众想象中的江户时代。<ref name=":1" />该资料片是在2016年10月拉斯维加斯举行的2016年最终幻想XIV粉丝节宣布的。<ref>{{Cite web|title=Stormblood is Final Fantasy 14’s next expansion|url=https://www.polygon.com/2016/10/14/13288196/final-fantasy-14-stormblood-announcement-reveal-release-date|accessdate=2020-12-05|date=2016-10-14|last=Kollar|first=Philip|work=Polygon|language=en|archive-date=2018-10-22|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181022042950/https://www.polygon.com/2016/10/14/13288196/final-fantasy-14-stormblood-announcement-reveal-release-date|dead-url=no}}</ref>关于资料片的更多细节在东京和法兰克福的活动中发布，包括发布日期，新职业，地点和副本。<ref>{{Cite web|title=Final Fantasy XIV Fan Festival Tokyo 2016: Red Mage, swimming, and Stormblood’s June 20 launch date {{!}} Massively Overpowered|url=https://massivelyop.com/2016/12/23/final-fantasy-xiv-fan-festival-tokyo-2016-red-mage-swimming-and-a-launch-date/|accessdate=2020-12-05|language=en-US|archive-date=2017-10-30|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20171030015358/http://massivelyop.com/2016/12/23/final-fantasy-xiv-fan-festival-tokyo-2016-red-mage-swimming-and-a-launch-date/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|title=Final Fantasy XIV Fan Festival XIV Europe: Samurai, Doma, and theme songs {{!}} Massively Overpowered|url=https://massivelyop.com/2017/02/18/final-fantasy-xiv-fan-festival-xiv-europe-samurai-doma-and-theme-songs/|accessdate=2020-12-05|language=en-US|archive-date=2017-11-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20171112050010/http://massivelyop.com/2017/02/18/final-fantasy-xiv-fan-festival-xiv-europe-samurai-doma-and-theme-songs/|dead-url=no}}</ref>

