18/11/final-fantasy-xv-x-final-fantasy-xiv-collaboration-quest-announced|accessdate=2020-12-05|date=2018-11-08|work=Gematsu|language=en-US|archive-date=2021-01-16|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210116112140/https://www.gematsu.com/2018/11/final-fantasy-xv-x-final-fantasy-xiv-collaboration-quest-announced|dead-url=no}}</ref>在这两款游戏中，玩家都与另一个版本的召唤兽战斗，以赢得新的装备和坐骑。<ref>{{Cite web|title=Final Fantasy XIV pre-expansion roadmap features a road trip with Noctis|url=https://www.rockpapershotgun.com/2019/02/04/final-fantasy-xiv-roadmap-includes-ff-xv-crossover/|accessdate=2020-12-05|date=2019-02-04|last=Tarason|first=Dominic|work=Rock, Paper, Shotgun|language=en-US|archive-date=2019-03-31|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190331051016/https://www.rockpapershotgun.com/2019/02/04/final-fantasy-xiv-roadmap-includes-ff-xv-crossover/|dead-url=no}}</ref>

