== 音乐 ==
除了担任音乐总监的职务外，[[祖坚正庆|祖坚正庆]]负责了资料片中大部分的音乐（超过100首曲目）。<ref name="#1">{{Cite web|title=STORMBLOOD: FINAL FANTASY XIV Original Soundtrack Out Now!|url=https://na.finalfantasyxiv.com/lodestone/topics/detail/1c1f368a0a8438f3e62d8f02d3c75fa2bba2bb85|accessdate=2020-12-05|last=Inc|first=SQUARE ENIX|work=FINAL FANTASY XIV, The Lodestone|language=en-us|archive-date=2020-06-15|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200615063827/https://na.finalfantasyxiv.com/lodestone/topics/detail/1c1f368a0a8438f3e62d8f02d3c75fa2bba2bb85|dead-url=no}}</ref>植松伸夫创作了两首音乐《Stormblood》和《Revolutions》。前者是与祖坚合作，后者则是游戏的主题曲。苏珊·卡洛威（Susan Calloway）以歌手的身份回归。<ref>{{Cite web|title=Final Fantasy XIV: Stormblood trailer reveals theme song and new in-game action|url=https://www.pcgamer.com/final-fantasy-xiv-stormblood-trailer-reveals-theme-song-and-new-in-game-action/|accessdate=2020-12-05|date=2017-05-16|last=Chalk|first=Andy|work=PC Gamer|language=en-US|archive-date=2020-11-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201112005933/https://www.pcgamer.com/final-fantasy-xiv-stormblood-trailer-reveals-theme-song-and-new-in-game-action/|dead-url=no}}</ref>祖坚以“武装优先和入侵”作为配乐的中心思想，将强大的军事侵略与这种侵略的“接收端”进行了对比。<ref name=":7">{{Cite web|title=Masayoshi Soken Interview: Heavensward and Beyond|url=http://www.vgmonline.net/masayoshisoken2/|accessdate=2020-12-05|date=2017-05-08|work=VGMO -Video Game Music Online-|language=en-US|archive-date=2018-11-17|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181117125910/http://www.vgmonline.net/masayoshisoken2/|dead-url=no}}</ref>一个例子是阿拉米格国歌《The Measure of His Reach》。它有两个版本，一个是原始版本，另一个是在加雷马占领下使用的版本，具有更尖锐的声音和更猛烈的歌词。<ref name=":3" />资料片的主要乐想在不同配乐中多次出现，在整个配乐中贯穿以匹配剧情。<ref name=":8">{{Cite web|title=Famitsu Talks to Soken About the Music in Stormblood|url=https://gamerescape.com/2018/03/20/famitsu-talks-to-soken-about-the-music-in-stormblood/|accessdate=2020-12-05|date=2018-03-20|last=O'Donnell|first=Jennifer|work=Gamer Escape: Gaming News, Reviews, Wikis, and Podcasts|language=en-US|archive-date=2021-03-01|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210301013137/https://gamerescape.com/2018/03/20/famitsu-talks-to-soken-about-the-music-in-stormblood/|dead-url=no}}</ref>由于这种设置，祖坚将亚洲乐器融入了他的编排中，并削减了场景音乐中使用的乐器数量，例如仅具有[[豎琴|竖琴]]和[[胡弓|胡弓]]的延夏主题曲。<ref name=":8" /><ref name=":7" />他为神龙和月读的原始boss战斗主题曲所做的工作感到特别自豪，这些主题曲分别属于红莲之狂潮主题和延夏主题。月度的战斗主题曲的每个阶段都引用了夜露生活的不同方面。<ref>{{Cite web|title=Masayoshi Soken Interview: Songs of Salt and Suffering|url=http://www.vgmonline.net/masayoshisokeninterview3/|accessdate=2020-12-05|date=2019-06-26|work=VGMO -Video Game Music Online-|language=en-US|archive-date=2020-01-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200108113226/http://www.vgmonline.net/masayoshisokeninterview3/|dead-url=no}}</ref>这个主题曲《任性的女儿》在员工投票中获得最高票数，从而成为《最终幻想XIV最佳音乐》合辑选择曲目。<ref>{{Cite web|title=Pre-Order FFXIV - The Best (The Best, The Best, The Best!) {{!}} FINAL FANTASY XIV: Developers’ Blog(na)|url=https://na.finalfantasyxiv.com/blog/002521.html|accessdate=2020-12-05|work=FINAL FANTASY XIV|language=en-us|archive-date=2020-11-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201112013547/https://na.finalfantasyxiv.com/blog/002521.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>

《最终幻想XIV：红莲之狂潮》原声大碟收集了从资料片发布到4.3补丁“月光之下”之间的音乐。 这张专辑由史克威尔艾尼克斯于2018年7月4日发行蓝光版，其中包含独占“ Wind-up Tsukuyomi”游戏内宠物。<ref name="#1"/>

