f>在[[OpenCritic|OpenCritic]]的39条评测中，有92％推荐该游戏，平均得分88。<ref>{{Cite web|title=Final Fantasy XIV: Stormblood Critic Reviews|url=https://opencritic.com/game/3939/final-fantasy-xiv-stormblood/charts|accessdate=2020-12-05|work=OpenCritic|language=en|archive-date=2018-11-01|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181101051459/http://opencritic.com/game/3939/final-fantasy-xiv-stormblood|dead-url=no}}</ref>在日本，首周主机版销量33000份，成为该地区当周最畅销的视频游戏。<ref>{{Cite web|title=Media Create Sales: 6/19/17 – 6/25/17|url=https://www.gematsu.com/2017/06/media-create-sales-61917-62517|accessdate=2020-12-05|date=2017-06-28|work=Gematsu|language=en-US|archive-date=2021-01-16|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210116115231/https://www.gematsu.com/2017/06/media-create-sales-61917-62517|dead-url=no}}</ref>在销售、反响和玩家人数方面，它超出了开发人员的期望。<ref name=":1" />

对故事剧情的好评在评论中很普遍。[[USgamer|USgamer]]的Mike Williams称赞游戏在展现叙事的复杂性和增加对角色的情感投入方面的克制，称其为“慢烧”。<ref name=":9">{{Cite web|title=Final Fantasy XIV: Stormblood Review: A Revolution That Lives Up To the 'Final Fantasy' Name|url=https://www.usgamer.net/articles/final-fantasy-xiv-stormblood-review|accessdate=2020-12-05|date=2017-07-01|last=3|work=USgamer|language=en|archive-date=2019-01-18|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190118232451/https://www.usgamer.net/articles/final-fantasy-xiv-stormblood-review|dead-url=no}}</ref>[[Kotaku|Kotaku]]的Mike Fahey认为游戏在保持快节奏和保持玩家的动力方面做得很好。<ref name=":10">{{Cite web|title=Final Fantasy XIV Stormblood: The Kotaku Review|url=https://kotaku.com/final-fantasy-xiv-stormblood-the-kotaku-review-1796771052|accessdate=2020-12-05|work=Kotaku|language=en-us|archive-date=2018-11-14|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181114215744/https://kotaku.com/final-fantasy-xiv-stormblood-the-kotaku-review-1796771052|dead-url=no}}</ref>[[Eurogamer|Eurogamer]]的Simon Parkin感谢吉田对故事基调的影响。<ref name=":11">{{Cite web|title=Final Fantasy 14 Stormblood review|url=https://www.eurogamer.net/articles/2017-06-03-final-fantasy-14-stormblood-review|accessdate=2020-12-05|date=2017-07-03|last=Parkin|first=Simon|work=Eurogamer|language=en|archive-date=2020-06-10|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200610113522/https://www.eurogamer.net/articles/2017-06-03-final-fantasy-14-stormblood-review|dead-url=no}}</ref>许多评论特别提到游戏中有关战争和殖民主义性质的主题，以示特别赞扬。<ref name=":12">{{Cite web|title=Final Fantasy 14: Stormblood Review|url=https://www.gamespot.com/reviews/final-fantasy-14-stormblood-review/1900-6416712/|accessdate=2020-12-05|work=GameSpot|language=en-US|archive-date=2019-04-29|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190429042021/https://www.gamespot.com/reviews/final-fantasy-14-stormblood-review/1900-6416712/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name=":13">{{Citation|title=Final Fantasy XIV: Stormblood Review - IGN|url=https://www.ign.com/articles/2017/06/30/final-fantasy-xiv-stormblood-review|accessdate=2020-12-05|language=en|archive-date=2019-04-29|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190429021100/https://www.ign.com/articles/2017/06/30/final-fantasy-xiv-stormblood-review|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name=":9" />包括[[GamesRadar+|GamesRadar+]]的Williams和Sam Prell在内的其他人则指出，出色的反派表现是故事的福音。<ref name=":14">{{Cite web|title=Final Fantasy 14: Stormblood review: "FF14 at the top of its storytelling game"|url=https://www.gamesradar.com/final-fantasy-14-ff14-stormblood-review/|accessdate=2020-12-05|last=July 2017|first=Sam Prell 20|work=Offical PlayStation Magazine|language=en|archive-date=2019-04-29|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190429042023/https://www.gamesradar.com/final-fantasy-14-ff14-stormblood-review/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name=":9" />

对游戏节奏的其他方面的反应则参差不齐。尽管Fahey认为它们的多样性是对先前扩展的改进，但大多数批评家都认为仍然缺少新的支线任务。<ref name=":9" /><ref name=":11" /><ref name=":10" />因此，Prell感到故事任务之间的磨合不平衡，[[IGN|IGN]]的Leif Johnson和[[PC_Gamer|PC Gamer]]的Steven Messner也提出了批评。<ref name=":14" /><ref name=":13" /><ref name=":15">{{Cite web|title=Final Fantasy 14: Stormblood review|url=https://www.pcgamer.com/final-fantasy-14-stormblood-review/|accessdate=2020-12-05|date=2017-06-27|last=Messner|first=Steven|work=PC Gamer|language=en-US|archive-date=2019-04-29|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190429042024/https://www.pcgamer.com/final-fantasy-14-stormblood-review/|dead-url=no}}</ref>另一方面，评论者建议玩家避免使用付费的剧情包和直升包，自己推进故事。<ref name=":14" /><ref name=":15" /><ref name=":11" />

游戏的战斗系统的各个方面都受到了普遍的赞誉。 [[Destructoid|Destructoid]]的Chris Carter将战斗遭遇描述为“新潮且引人入胜”，Prell和Messner对须佐之男歼灭战印象深刻，后者将其与《[[合金装备崛起_复仇|合金装备崛起]]》进行了比较。<ref>{{Cite web|title=Review: Final Fantasy XIV: Stormblood|url=https://www.destructoid.com/stories/review-final-fantasy-xiv-stormblood-442923.phtml|accessdate=2020-12-05|work=Destructoid|language=en|archive-date=2020-11-15|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201115123629/https://www.destructoid.com/stories/review-final-fantasy-xiv-stormblood-442923.phtml|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name=":14" /><ref name=":15" />在战斗中，系统级的变更也得到了广泛接受，包括简化角色动作和职业解锁，<ref name=":10" />合并未充分使用的统计数据和职业量谱界面。<ref name=":16">{{Cite web|title=Review: Final Fantasy XIV: Stormblood|url=https://www.destructoid.com/stories/review-final-fantasy-xiv-stormblood-442923.phtml|accessdate=2020-12-05|work=Destructoid|language=en|archive-date=2020-11-15|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201115123629/https://www.destructoid.com/stories/review-final-fantasy-xiv-stormblood-442923.phtml|dead-url=no}}</ref>评论的另一个一致点是对两个新职业赤魔法师和武士的称赞。赤魔法师的近战和远程攻击交织在一起，赢得了热烈的反响，武士的连击系统倍受赞誉，两者均因提供独特的游戏体验而受到赞扬。<ref name=":16" /><ref name=":12" /><ref name=":15" /><ref name=":10" />最后，Carter和Messner赞美了PvP的改进，Messner称这是“我在《红莲之狂潮》中最喜欢的活动之一”。<ref name=":16" /><ref name=":15" />

评论称赞此资料片的艺术和环境设计。<ref name=":14" /><ref name=":10" />[[GameSpot|GameSpot]]的Ginny Woo认为，以亚洲为主题的区域已被“很好地整合”到故事中。<ref name=":12" />Johnson在受蒙古启发的太阳神草原的荒野中看到了“创造力的新高峰”。<ref name=":16" />Carter指出，PlayStation 4 Pro的4K分辨率模式是一项令人印象深刻的功能。<ref name=":16" />游泳模式的增加，添加了游戏的热情。尽管Fahey认为水下环境在视觉上很吸引人，但他得出的结论是，这种环境“没有得到充分利用”，Carter对此表示赞同。<ref name=":16" /><ref name=":12" />

总体而言，评论家称《红莲之狂潮》雨是《苍穹之禁城》堂的一种改进。<ref name=":9" /><ref name=":11" /><ref name=":10" />Fahey指出，这款游戏是“能够维持每月订阅模式的少数MMORPG之一”。<ref name=":10" />卡特得出结论，资料片遵循了“与游戏本体相同的模式”，但承认“该模式是制胜法宝”。<ref name=":16" />在2017年，该资料片赢得了Game Informer， Bleeding Cool，和RPGamer的“最佳MMO”奖。 <ref>{{Cite web|title=Game Informer's Best Of 2017 Awards|url=https://www.gameinformer.com/b/features/archive/2018/01/04/game-informers-best-of-2017-awards.aspx|accessdate=2020-12-05|last=Staff|first=Game Informer|work=Game Informer|language=en|archive-date=2019-02-13|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190213103643/https://www.gameinformer.com/b/features/archive/2018/01/04/game-informers-best-of-2017-awards.aspx|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|title=Bleeding Cool Game Awards 2017: Best MMO|url=https://bleedingcool.com/games/bleeding-cool-game-awards-2017-best-mmo/|accessdate=2020-12-05|date=2017-12-31|last=Ricchiuto|first=Madeline|work=Bleeding Cool News And Rumors|language=en-US|archive-date=2021-01-25|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210125082003/https://bleedingcool.com/games/bleeding-cool-game-awards-2017-best-mmo/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|title=RPGamer > 2017 Awards Results > Best MMO|url=https://archive.rpgamer.com/awards/2017/mmo.html|accessdate=2020-12-05|work=archive.rpgamer.com|archive-date=2020-10-20|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201020151307/https://archive.rpgamer.com/awards/2017/mmo.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>也在PlayStation博客上获得了“最佳发布后内容”的编辑选择。<ref>{{Cite web|title=Game of the Year 2017: The Winners, As Voted By You|url=https://blog.playstation.com/2018/01/11/game-of-the-year-2017-the-winners-as-voted-by-you/|accessdate=2020-12-05|date=2018-01-11|work=PlayStation.Blog|language=en-US|archive-date=2021-02-27|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210227201659/https://blog.playstation.com/2018/01/11/game-of-the-year-2017-the-winners-as-voted-by-you/|dead-url=no}}</ref>在2018年，该资料片赢得了Massively OP颁发的“最佳MMO”奖。<ref>{{Cite web|title=Massively OP’s 2018 Awards: MMORPG of the Year {{!}} Massively Overpowered|url=https://massivelyop.com/2018/12/28/massively-ops-2018-awards-goty/|accessdate=2020-12-05|language=en-US|archive-date=2019-07-01|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190701052650/https://massivelyop.com/2018/12/28/massively-ops-2018-awards-goty/|dead-url=no}}</ref>

